{"tid":159770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最殘忍折磨人既方式係咩？","createTime":"2017-03-17T08:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T09:00:37.000Z","uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3da5b8e866b649ef2e181a549c68c2d4d99d56","tid":159770,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"曾經思考過依個問題<br />\n包括火燒，整盲，宮刑etc<br />\n但以上既虐待行為總會有一日康復 而且只要心理夠強大都會克服到<br />\n但最變態既應該係人彘 真正求生不得求死不能<br />\n比人救返 你連自殺既能力都無 日日訓係度得個腦係度運作唔知可以點 野又睇唔到 聽唔到 郁唔到 淨係個腦係咁loop<br />\n<br />\n所有犯嚴重罪行包括虐人/畜 強姦 etc都應該受依種刑<br />\n就算中東以眼還眼都係唔夠 要還夠十倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c79f1fd5009f79e01d6601052f8971433496afb","tid":159770,"uid":29742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:43:17.000Z","msg":"唔俾人訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33bc7144615d8d971d5e2a009a6f01f22d4bc96","tid":159770,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"綁住佢<br />\n唔俾佢郁<br />\n係佢面前放a片"},{"pid":"4f780947a39e7420df79e5d00fcba0f4b2782ccb","tid":159770,"uid":41302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"拎支針擺係佢龜頭離開小小距離 之後不停播咸片"},{"pid":"e2ad87a8dd7bb423f8da33e8d615ca0710942c3c","tid":159770,"uid":49607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:52:43.000Z","msg":"用象筋扎住佢條撚，再逼佢睇av令到佢充血"},{"pid":"972165c7c1c259f38d419c4c36ade6e01d5f32f1","tid":159770,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"挷住佢之後播gv<br />\n再搵幾個男人同佢互含，射到大家都成身精，成臉精，成口精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=